Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:07.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Like an angel that has no\Nsense of mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:14.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Rise, young boy, to the heavens\Nlike a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:26.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Cold winds, as blue as the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:29.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Tear open the door to\Nyour heart, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:33.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But unknowing you seem, just\Nstaring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:37.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Standing there smiling serenely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Desperate, for something to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,A moment of kindness like\Nthat in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:48.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your innocent eyes, have yet no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:51.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Of the path your destiny will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But someday you’ll become aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Everything that you’ve got behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your wings are for seeking out a new...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:06.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Future that only you can search for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:14.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis enters through\Nthe window of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:18.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,If you should betray the chapel\Nof your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:21.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis bleeds through\Na portal like your pulsing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:25.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,So, boy, stand tall and embrace\Nthe fire of the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:29.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Embracing the universe like\Na blazing star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:39.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you refusing to allow us to question\Nthe pilot of Unit 01, the only one directly\Ninvolved in the incident, Major Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because he is emotionally very unstable...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...I believe that it would be unwise\Nto have him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:48.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, as his proxy, let us ask you,\NMajor Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:54.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In this incident, didn’t the Angel attempt\Nto communicate with a human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I find no suggestion of that\Nin the subject’s report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:00.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I believe this was an irregularity,\Na coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If, and only if, his memory is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There is no evidence that his memory\Nhas been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:09.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, the Eva’s AC recorder was not\Nfunctioning.  There’s no way to confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:13.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Was the Angel interested in the\Nhuman spirit?  In the human mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am unable to answer that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Whether the Angels even have a\Nconcept of what “mind” is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...or whether they can understand\Nhuman thoughts or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...is completely unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:27.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A new factor has been added with\Nthis incident, in that the Angel\Ntried to take Eva into itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:33.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is there any possibility that this\Naspect may be linked to the predicted\NThirteenth Angel and all Angels thereafter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:37.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Based on the previous patterns, there\Nwould appear to be no systematic\Norganization among the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:42.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That is correct!  It is indeed obvious that\Nthey have worked independently, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You are not allowed to ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:47.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That will be all.  Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angels appear to be getting\Nmore and more intelligent.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,There’s not much time left.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.66,Background,,0,0,0,Video Text,{\1c&H000000&\p1}m 0 0 l 720 0 720 540 0 540
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.66,Episode (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,230)}Episode 17:
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.66,Title (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7)}{\pos(360,257)}The 4th Child
Dialogue: 4,0:02:59.54,0:03:02.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,Left for us, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who’s the patient in Room 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:11.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s the emergency room patient\Nfrom the first Eva incident.\NShe’s been here for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:14.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Her injuries were very severe, poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’s still in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s here again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:22.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, he comes to see her\Nat least twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s a good brother,\Nthinking about his sister like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:27.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, boys like that are pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He has a good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei, are you all right today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.  I will be with Dr. Akagi tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And the day after I’ll be at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How is school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:42.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No problems, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.  That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:49.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stand up!  Bow!  Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:54.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let me see, Ayanami is absent\Nas usual, and Aida, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:55.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s up with Kensuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Professor Koike is absent today...\N\N\N{\c&H00E3FE&}What’s up with Kensuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Professor Koike is absent today...\N{\c&H00E3FE&}He went to New Yokosuka,\Nto see a battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}...so modern Japanese will be self-study.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}He went to New Yokosuka,\Nto see a battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:01.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}...so modern Japanese will be self-study.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}A ship called Myoko or something\Nlike that is in port.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}And finally, the student on duty today is...\N{\c&H00E3FE&}A ship called Myoko or something\Nlike that is in port.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:04.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mister Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Y...yes, sir!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:09.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Will you deliver this document to\NMiss Ayanami after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, First Branch is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:20.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The data from the recon plane will\Nbe confirmed by the MAGI.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The entire Second Branch just vanished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.  It’s been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Dear God...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Administrative and Investigative\Nsections are going crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and General Affairs is in a total panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What was the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s still under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:43.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Our only clues are these recon photos\Nfrom the geosynchronous satellite.\NThere’s nothing else left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,10 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,8...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,7...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,6...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,5...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:52.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:53.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:54.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:13.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 04, its support group and\Nall other facilities within an 89 km radius\Nwere completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Along with thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Looking at the time schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:22.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...it would appear that they were in\Nthe middle of installing the experimental\NS2 engine from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:26.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Potential causes range from insufficient\Nstructural integrity to a calculation error\Nduring the preliminary design stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:29.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s 32,768 possibilities right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And that’s not mentioning sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But it wasn’t an explosion, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was a “disappearance.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:40.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In all probability, they were swallowed by\Na Sea of Dirac, just like Unit 01 was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And the restored S2 engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Gone.  Along with our hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:48.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s all because we’re being forced to use\Nthings that we don’t really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Things like the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’ll we do with Unit 03?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll receive it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The US government doesn’t want to\Nlose the First Branch as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:04.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Didn’t they insist on the right to\Nbuild Units 03 and 04?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:09.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And now they’re foisting it off on us?\NThey’re really pushing their luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:12.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,After a disaster like that,\Nanyone would get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And how are you going to\Ndo the test activation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Will you use Rei’s dummy plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the dummy plug prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei’s personal data has\Nbeen loaded into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:29.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but it’s not really possible to digitize\Na human mind and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A fake, that’s all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It copies a pilot’s thinking process.\NIn the end, it’s only a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It transmits a signal pattern to Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:43.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and Eva believes that there is a pilot\Nand synchronizes.  That’s good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Load the data into Unit 01 and Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There are still some problems with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s not important.  As long as the\NEva activates, it’s sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve delegated the transportation\Nof the unit to the UN.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It will arrive by the end of the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ll take care of it from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll perform the modifications and\Nactivation test in Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And the test pilot will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Use of the dummy plug is not\Nrecommended at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,One of our prospective candidates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...will be chosen as the Fourth Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There is one child whose core can\Nbe prepared immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then, I’ll trust you to make it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei, we’re finished now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stand up!  Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:42.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lunch time!  Lunch time!\NThis is the single best thing about school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You didn’t make lunches for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I didn’t have time to cook last night.\NI had too much homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And that’s your excuse for me having\Nto go without lunch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A husband and wife quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s not like that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is it?  You look so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s the Unit 03 activation test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:12.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll be using the Fourth as the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Fourth Child’s been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But I haven’t received a report from\Nthe Marduk Institute yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The official documents will be\Ndelivered tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:30.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Dr. Akagi, are you hiding something\Nfrom me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:35.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, okay.  So, who’s the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Christ!  It’s HIM?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All of the prospective candidates have\Nbeen gathered together to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s so hard to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:54.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka will be fine.\NShe’s committed to piloting an Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei is exceptional...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:09:00.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...with no problems with her Eva\Nor our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:04.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji probably knows the most\Nabout the down side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t want him to suffer\Nany more hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But we need children of this kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...in order for us all to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you saying not to\Ncomplicate the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Bye!  Later!  See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Suzuhara!  You’ve got the duty\Nthis week, get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The class printout!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Didn’t our teacher tell you to deliver this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come on, Class Rep, you can ask the\Nother person on duty, can’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Miss Ayanami is absent today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ayanami and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then I guess there’s no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:46.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But I don’t want to go to some\Ngirl’s place all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I can go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Walk home with me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:20.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You can’t enter a girl’s room\Nwithout her permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ve got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She won’t see it if we leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:43.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this a girl’s room?  It’s so decrepit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey!  You shouldn’t touch anything!\NShe’ll get pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m just cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I won’t help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s not a man’s job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay, but Misato hates guys like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t care!  It’s my policy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.92,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you’ve changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The first time I saw you,\NI really thought you were a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You didn’t seem like someone who’d\Ndo something for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:43.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I guess you’re just really reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:55.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Those are the school bulletins\Nthat have piled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:07.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I took it upon myself to clean up a little.\NBut I didn’t touch anything except trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:12.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Th...thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:21.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva pilots are sure weird all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Words of gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Words I’ve never used...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not even to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:52.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The city, a paradise made by mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Driven from Paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:58.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...man escaped to this earthly existence,\Non the edge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Created by the weakest of beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:06.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...created by the sapience born from that\Nweakness, this paradise is our creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.85,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,To protect ourselves from the fear\Nthat death instills...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...to satiate our beings with pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:14.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...we create a paradise by\Nand of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:20.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This city surely is such a paradise.\NA city armed to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:24.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A city for those who run in fear from the\Noutside world, the world of our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But cowards do live longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s to our benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:35.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The third New Tokyo,\NNERV’s hidden intercept base...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:39.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the long delayed seventh construction\Nphase will soon be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,At long last, it will be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 04’s “accident,” how will you\Nreport it to the committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,With the facts, the cause is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:57.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But this is a major, catastrophic loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 04 and the Second Branch\Nare of no consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:04.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The S2 engine prototype may have\Nbeen lost, but the data is still on\Nrecord in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This installation and Unit 01\Nwill be sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:10.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But the committee is in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course, it was an\Nunscheduled accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:17.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,SEELE must be busy changing\Nthe schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Incidents not depicted in the\NDead Sea Scrolls may occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This ought to teach the old men a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:27.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}3rd District Transformation & Directional\NWeapon experiment is on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The intercept system is completed...\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,The intercept system is completed...\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Will Dr. Nishizono of the Technical\NDepartment, Section 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,...and they’re not going to have a party?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Will Dr. Nishizono of the Technical\NDepartment, Section 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,...and they’re not going to have a party?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}...call Section 2 of the Development\NDivision immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,NERV is the most inflexible organization.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}...call Section 2 of the Development\NDivision immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,NERV is the most inflexible organization.\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s because of Commander Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And are you a prude, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:45.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll tell Miss Katsuragi and Dr. Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not if your mouth is covered with mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, how’s it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, it’s going, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I have work to do.  Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:58.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Far be it from me to make judgments\Non your private life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:02.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but under these circumstances should\Nyou be hitting on girls in this organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who’s under whom isn’t your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or would you prefer I hit\Non you, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It depends on how you\Nanswer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You know the secrets behind the\NMarduk Institute and that Adam thing\Ndown there, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:13.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t try to feign ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asking for help isn’t like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You know, at the moment I don’t care,\NI’m not feeling very reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:25.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Fourth Child was conveniently\Nfound at just the right time.\NWhat’s the truth behind that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:34.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Marduk Institute doesn’t exist.\NNERV is pulling the strings all by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,NERV itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You need to check Code 707.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Code 707?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji’s school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:49.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ritsuko says she’s expecting you for a\Nmeeting about tomorrow’s business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All right.  Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:54.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Buy you a drink?  Cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But...  I’m a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:10.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I thought you’d be a more\Nserious person, Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re saying that to someone as arrow\Nstraight and reliable as me, Shinji Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I...I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:19.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, too.\NI didn’t mean to sound rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Watermelons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, aren’t they cute?  This is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Keep it a secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:38.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Growing...  making something\Ngrow is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,One can see and learn so many\Nthings from the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It also brings pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But pain, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you hate pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But have you found what\Ngives you pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.05,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:02.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you’ve known pain and hardship,\Nit’s easier to be kind to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Being kind isn’t a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes?  Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The synch test will be starting soon.
