Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The pilot will be officially\Ninformed tomorrow.\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stand up!  Attention!  Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Attention student Toji Suzuhara...\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,Toji Suzuhara...\NReport to the Principal’s Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I’m Toji Suzuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re Toji Suzuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How was your trip to New Yokosuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Way cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:11.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I picked up\Nsome disturbing information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 03?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:18.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, the one they built in America.\NIt’s completed, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:23.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know it’s classified,\Nbut please tell me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I really don’t know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:29.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Haven’t you heard the rumor that the\Nactivation test will be held at the second\Ntest facility in Matsushiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I haven’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The pilot hasn’t been chosen yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato could pick me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:42.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, would you ask her for me?\NI really want to be an Eva pilot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really, I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:49.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about the story that\NUnit 04’s been lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You really don’t know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It disappeared along with the\Nentire Second Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My dad’s section was in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato didn’t tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:07.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it doesn’t directly\Nconcern the pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:11.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If she didn’t tell you, it’s probably because\Nyou don’t need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry about bothering you\Nwith weird questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But Toji hasn’t come back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:26.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thus, we, mankind, survived the hell\Ncalled the Second Impact and rose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The number of children has been\Ndecreasing yearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sorry I’m late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know about it.  Be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:38.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anyway, it is you, the younger\Ngenerations, who will lead the\Nway to the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.01,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about Toji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’ll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s got class duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:01.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The school is now closing.  All students\Nmust go to their homes immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Suzuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:06.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Line up the desks and write up\Nthe daily record!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:14.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I haven’t had lunch yet.\NI’ll do it as soon as I’ve eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Suzuhara, you always buy your lunch\Nfrom the school shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s because there’s no one\Nwho cooks for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Suzuhara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:29.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have two sisters.  Their names\Nare Kodama and Nozomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and I always cook lunch for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That must be a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:38.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, I’m actually a good cook,\Nthough you might not think it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:39.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And I always end up cooking\Ntoo much for our lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you need help getting rid of\Nyour leftovers, I’ll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:00.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, Asuka?  Sorry, I’m busy right now.\NCan it wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:08.40,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But you have time to\Nsee Misato, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!  Not right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,These are our synch data reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Four of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What in the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:25.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who made HIM the Fourth Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:28.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  I don’t understand!  What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:11.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 03 is delivered\Nto Matsushiro from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:15.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,People glory in the last peaceful day,\Nunaware of the coming tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,On that day, all eyes will be focused\Non the children’s tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:23.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The quiet days that collusion has\Ncamouflaged are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:26.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and Misato’s heart is filled with the\Nsound of Shinji screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s the next episode,\N“The Judgment of Life.”
Dialogue: 5,0:23:29.44,0:23:32.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,And I’ll give you lots of fan service again!
